claim.claim-text:
20. A heat sink assembly comprising:
a circuit board;
a central processing unit mounted to the circuit board;
a voltage regulator module mounted to the central processing unit, wherein the central processing unit and the voltage regulator are mounted in a stacked relation to one another on a common side of the circuit board;
a first heat sink engaged to and in thermal communication with the central processing unit; and
a second beat sink surrounded by said first heat sink, said second heat sink engaged to and in thermal communication with the voltage regulator module.
